Tests

Success

{% raw %} 
input_ = {'username': 'Delgg4', 'password': '12765'}
event = Event.getInput(body = input_)
signIn(event)

{'body': '{}',
 'statusCode': 200,
 'headers': {'Access-Control-Allow-Headers': '*',
  'Access-Control-Allow-Origin': '*',
  'Access-Control-Allow-Methods': '*'}}
{% endraw %}

Failure

Invalid Password

{% raw %} 
input_1 = {'username': 'Delgg4', 'password': '1276'}
event = Event.getInput(body = input_1)
signIn(event)

{'body': '{"error":"incorrect password "}',
 'statusCode': 400,
 'headers': {'Access-Control-Allow-Headers': '*',
  'Access-Control-Allow-Origin': '*',
  'Access-Control-Allow-Methods': '*'}}
{% endraw %}

Invalid Username

{% raw %} 
input_1 = {'username': 'Delgg43', 'password': '1276'}
event = Event.getInput(body = input_1)
signIn(event)

{'body': '{"error":"username does not exist or is incorrect "}',
 'statusCode': 400,
 'headers': {'Access-Control-Allow-Headers': '*',
  'Access-Control-Allow-Origin': '*',
  'Access-Control-Allow-Methods': '*'}}
{% endraw %}
